hey! okay soO 2day was boring *slash* scary *slash* amazingly fun at the same time!! lol okay soO.. Eric left about an hour or 2 after that =( *Cries* anywho, me and Amanda chilled here for a while.. talked about stuff and ppl.. and read stuff.. and listeneed to music.. lol and then we were talking, and i remembered i had a little box in my room on my shelf of stuff.. that Amanda gave me a present in, and when she and her x.Boyfriend Tim Foster were going out.. lol and on the inside of the bottom part of the box she wrote *T.f + A.w*12.8.03* lol soO anyways, i showed that 2 her and she was like *Lets burn it!* lol sooooo we went 2 the Golf Course acrossed the street from my house, we went there, and took the box, along with sum matches =) lol anyways, soO were trying to lite the stupid thing.... and it wont lite! okay soO we go back 2 my house real quick 2 get sum rubbing alcohol/perfume/and nail polish remover.... and go back 2 the golf course, and dump the stuff in it, then lite it!.. Okay..? soooooo.. like less than a minute after we lite the f.cking thing.. i turn around and see my f.cking neighbor walking her dumb dog, like.. half a quartor of a mile behind us.. and im like "Sh.t!...
